<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>储蓄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每每银行利放宽，囊中羞涩愧连连。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一张卡里家山重，欲把青春存万年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>忆那年班花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">麻花小辫俏佳人，手捧书来倍认真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">预备铃声刚响起，身姿挺立正青春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>偶遇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相逢那日雨中人，一伞荷塘撑到分。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万语千言惟有泪，只缘各已束终身。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>忆初恋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一笑嫣然俩酒窝，芙蓉粉面喜哼歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">银铃声里藏魔力，勾起青春那爱河。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>忆自行车走江湖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北陌南山一路情，朝霞作伴晚披星。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">单车脚踩三千里，湿透胶东半岛风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>儿时上学路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晨雾天光一路开，书包鼓鼓幸福塞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铃声预备青春梦，片片红霞挤进怀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>儿时放学路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三三两两校门飞，笑语盈盈爬上眉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路斜阳抛脑后，炊烟唤我乳名归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">樱娇杏粉各争妍，未许东君一刻闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不信细听杨柳下，春之鸟语也斑斓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>手机伴侣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浪迹江湖不再孤，寻词觅句悟沉浮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寸屏里面乾坤大，日月星辰尽画图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>地摊又火</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芹绿椒红采北坡，熙熙攘攘笑容多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今扫码成时尚，支付人生一首歌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>娘亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿针引线苦持家，晚补星星早补霞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">担水南园挑日月，终生莫忘是咱妈。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泡茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一壶汤色话人生，数叶浮沉戏水清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坎坷几番方品味，原来阅历最真情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老辗深情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老辗沉沉梦里头，乾坤转转幸福收。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">磨出最美浓香味，似见娘亲汗水流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>老院赏桃花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人面桃花笑语裁，旧时光景院中开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年年三月娇娇媚，半个春天挤进来。</p>
<h1>《千家诗词》</h1>
<p>主编：郑万才</p>
<p>副主编：王惠玲、王天明、胡晓娜</p>
